OL,3,C'Their love story was rare': Inquest
OL,4,Cinto couple who drowned in flash
OL,5,Cflooding
OL,7,FThe daughter of an elderly couple who
OL,8,Flost their lives after their car
OL,9,Fbecame trapped in flood water has told
OL,10,Fa court there are no words that can
OL,11,Fdescribe her depth of grief.
OL,13,FElaine and Philip Marco were just a
OL,14,Ffew days away from celebrating their
OL,15,F54th wedding anniversary when they
OL,16,Fdied after their car became submerged
OL,17,Fin flash flooding under a railway
OL,18,Fbridge in a section of Queens Drive,
OL,19,Fin South Liverpool, on 26 August 2023.
