OL,3,C'Their love story was rare': Inquest
OL,4,Cinto couple who drowned in flash
OL,5,Cflooding
OL,7,FAs an inquest opened into the couple's
OL,8,Fdeaths members of the Marco family
OL,9,Fstruggled to hold back tears as
OL,10,Ftributes were paid to the much-loved
OL,11,Fpair.
OL,13,FThe couple's daughter Sarah, told the
OL,14,Finquest, in Liverpool, the loss of her
OL,15,Fparents was not just felt by her and
OL,16,Fher siblings, but their children as
OL,17,Fwell.
OL,19,FThe couple had 10 grandchildren and
OL,20,Fanother on the way, she said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
