OL,3,C'Their love story was rare': Inquest
OL,4,Cinto couple who drowned in flash
OL,5,Cflooding
OL,7,F"Their love story was rare, they spent
OL,8,Fevery waking moment together," she
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,FShe added the whole family felt robbed
OL,12,F- and revealed that the events of that
OL,13,Fday had left her with post traumatic
OL,14,Fstress disorder (PTSD).
OL,16,F"There are moments when I physically
OL,17,Fstruggle to breathe, as though the air
OL,18,Fhas been stolen from my lungs," she
OL,19,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
