OL,3,C'Their love story was rare': Inquest
OL,4,Cinto couple who drowned in flash
OL,5,Cflooding
OL,7,F"My heart aches constantly not
OL,8,Fmetaphorically, but in a real,
OL,9,Fphysical way. I now understand what it
OL,10,Fmeans to be truly broken-hearted."
OL,12,FThe couple had been at their son
OL,13,FJoshua's house celebrating his 40th
OL,14,Fbirthday before the accident happened,
OL,15,Fthe inquest was told.
OL,17,FTheir son Simon said that the hardest
OL,18,Fthing he had ever had to do in his
OL,19,Flife was to tell his children that
OL,20,Fboth of their grandparents had died
OL,21,Fsuddenly in such tragic circumstances.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
