OL,7,FIn his statement, he told the court:
OL,8,F"They were our foundation - without
OL,9,Fthem we feel un-anchoured."
OL,11,FSince the deaths a range of safety
OL,12,Fmeasures has been introduced around
OL,13,Fwhere the accident happened. The
OL,14,Fsection of Queens Drive was shut for
OL,15,Ffive months.
OL,17,FNew flood sensors were installed
OL,18,Falongside new signage and barriers.
